snippet: The man and the woman fell into the water during Fourth of July celebrations.
abstract: Bodies of Willie Tom and Celine Fu, who have been missing since they fell into water while riding Jet Ski during Fourth of July celebrations, are found at marina near Coney Island Creek.
lead_paragraph: The man and the woman fell into the water during Fourth of July celebrations.

headline.main: Bodies of 2 Jet Ski Riders Are Found at a Marina
headline.print_headline: Bodies of 2 Jet Ski Riders Are Found at a Marina
